title: Oscars 2017: Worst dressed on the red carpet | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad Color clash catastrophes, accidental exposures and garish gowns... FEMAIL spotlights the stars suffering serious style disasters on the red carpet at the 89th Academy Awards Stars hoping to pick up a statue at Sunday's Oscar's ceremony in Hollywood didn't all start the night off with a bang, arriving on the red carpet in some sartorial setbacks Leading the way on this year's worst-dressed list is actresses Leslie Mann and Blanca Blanco, as well as screenwriter Allison Schroeder Published: 00:20 GMT, 27 February 2017 | Updated: 01:58 GMT, 27 February 2017 79 shares
